<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Exerciselog app!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <!-- You can add your company logo here -->
    <!-- <img src="logo.png" alt="Company logo" class="logo"> -->
    <h1>Welcome <%= name %>!</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>We're excited to have you join our Exerciselog community!</p>

    <p>Your account has been successfully created with email: <strong><%= email %></strong> and you can now start using our service. We've prepared a few tips to help you get started:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Complete your profile by adding more information about yourself</li>
      <li>Track your daily exercises and progress</li>
      <li>Explore our latest features and capabilities</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button">Log In Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Best regards,<br>
      The Exerciselog Team</p>

    <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Exerciselog. All rights reserved.</p>

    <p>You are receiving this email because you created an account with email: <%= email %>.<br>
      If this wasn't you, please ignore this message or contact us.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>